<p style="margin:0 0 16px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.6;color:#3f4a3c;">Hi <%= @user.display_name %> 👋🏻</p>

<p style="margin:0 0 16px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.6;color:#3f4a3c;">
  Welcome to the Turf Monster newsletter — you'll be first to hear about new contests,
  new games, and prizes.
</p>

<p style="margin:0 0 28px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.6;color:#3f4a3c;">
